content.main_review:
Strengths:

- The method adapts to new tasks autonomously;
- Ablation study and comparison with supervised models;
- Exhaustive implementation details in the Appendix section.

Weaknesses: 

- Experimental analysis is limited to image and video datasets;
- The mIoU metric is never defined in the paper;
- Fairly limited scope of competitor methods (which could depend on the limited suitability of other methods in the adopted setting).

